<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>TripKorea - 커뮤니티</title>
  {{>partials/head-assets}}
</head>
<body class="community-list-body-01">
  {{>partials/header}}

<main class="page-main-wrap-1440">
<div class="layout-stack-960">
<div class="community-list-div-01">
<div class="stack-gap-2">
<h1 class="community-list-h1-01">커뮤니티</h1>
<p class="community-list-p-01">
                        여행자들과 함께 소통하며 대한민국 곳곳의 여행 팁과 숨은 명소를 발견해 보세요.
                    </p>
</div>
<button class="community-list-button-01">
<span class="icon-ms-20">edit</span>
<span>글쓰기</span>
</button>
</div>
<div class="community-list-div-02">
<div class="community-list-div-03">
<div class="chips-scroll-mask">
<button class="community-list-button-02">
                            전체
                        </button>
<button class="chip-filter-btn">
                            여행 팁
                        </button>
<button class="chip-filter-btn">
                            여행 계획
                        </button>
<button class="chip-filter-btn">
                            맛집/카페
                        </button>
<button class="chip-filter-btn">
                            숙소 후기
                        </button>
<button class="chip-filter-btn">
                            질문/답변
                        </button>
</div>
<button class="community-list-button-03">
<span class="icon-ms-18">restart_alt</span>
                        필터 초기화
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="stack-gap-3">
<div class="place-card-row">
<div class="community-list-div-04">
<div class="inline-row-gap2-mb2">
<span class="community-list-span-01">
                                질문
                            </span>
<span class="community-list-span-02">• 2시간 전</span>
</div>
<h3 class="place-card-title">
                            서귀포에서 작업하기 좋은 와이파이 빵빵한 카페 추천해 주세요
                        </h3>
<p class="text-muted-sm-truncate">
                            제주도에서 일주일 정도 원격 근무를 할 예정입니다. 조용하고 콘센트가 많은 곳을 찾고 있어요...
                        </p>
</div>
<div class="place-card-meta">
<div class="inline-row-gap1-5">
<span class="icon-ms-18">visibility</span>
<span>1.2k</span>
</div>
<div class="community-list-div-05">
<span class="icon-ms-18">chat_bubble</span>
<span>24</span>
</div>
<div class="inline-row-gap2-ml2">
<div class="avatar-xs" data-alt="User avatar placeholder"></div>
<span class="text-main-xs-medium">nomad_kim</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="place-card-row">
<div class="community-list-div-04">
<div class="inline-row-gap2-mb2">
<span class="community-list-span-03">
                                리뷰
                            </span>
<span class="community-list-span-02">• 5시간 전</span>
</div>
<h3 class="place-card-title">
                            홍대 숨은 재즈바 '블루노트' 꼭 가보세요
                        </h3>
<p class="text-muted-sm-truncate">
                            대학교 근처 지하에 있는 정말 멋진 재즈바를 발견했어요. 라이브 공연은 저녁 9시부터 시작해요.
                        </p>
</div>
<div class="place-card-meta">
<div class="inline-row-gap1-5">
<span class="icon-ms-18">visibility</span>
<span>856</span>
</div>
<div class="inline-row-hover-primary">
<span class="icon-ms-18">chat_bubble</span>
<span>12</span>
</div>
<div class="inline-row-gap2-ml2">
<div class="avatar-xs" data-alt="User avatar placeholder"></div>
<span class="text-main-xs-medium">jazz_lover</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="place-card-row">
<div class="community-list-div-04">
<div class="inline-row-gap2-mb2">
<span class="community-list-span-04">
                                주의사항
                            </span>
<span class="community-list-span-02">• 어제</span>
</div>
<h3 class="place-card-title">
                            이번 주말 해운대 호우 주의보 발령
                        </h3>
<p class="text-muted-sm-truncate">
                            해변으로 가기 전에 예보를 꼭 확인하세요. 일부 행사가 취소될 수 있습니다.
                        </p>
</div>
<div class="place-card-meta">
<div class="inline-row-gap1-5">
<span class="icon-ms-18">visibility</span>
<span>3.4k</span>
</div>
<div class="inline-row-hover-primary">
<span class="icon-ms-18">chat_bubble</span>
<span>45</span>
</div>
<div class="inline-row-gap2-ml2">
<div class="avatar-xs" data-alt="User avatar placeholder"></div>
<span class="text-main-xs-medium">weather_bot</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="place-card-row">
<div class="community-list-div-04">
<div class="inline-row-gap2-mb2">
<span class="community-list-span-05">
                                일정
                            </span>
<span class="community-list-span-02">• 2일 전</span>
</div>
<h3 class="place-card-title">
                            뚜벅이 여행자를 위한 경주 1박 2일 역사 투어 코스
                        </h3>
<p class="text-muted-sm-truncate">
                            대중교통만 이용해서 불국사와 안압지를 방문하는 상세 가이드입니다.
                        </p>
</div>
<div class="place-card-meta">
<div class="inline-row-gap1-5">
<span class="icon-ms-18">visibility</span>
<span>2.1k</span>
</div>
<div class="inline-row-hover-primary">
<span class="icon-ms-18">chat_bubble</span>
<span>89</span>
</div>
<div class="inline-row-gap2-ml2">
<div class="avatar-xs" data-alt="User avatar placeholder"></div>
<span class="text-main-xs-medium">history_buff</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="place-card-row">
<div class="community-list-div-04">
<div class="inline-row-gap2-mb2">
<span class="community-list-span-01">
                                질문
                            </span>
<span class="community-list-span-02">• 3일 전</span>
</div>
<h3 class="place-card-title">
                            겨울에 속초 여행 갈만한가요?
                        </h3>
<p class="text-muted-sm-truncate">
                            겨울 바다 여행으로 속초랑 강릉 중에 고민 중입니다. 추천해 주실 만한 곳 있나요?
                        </p>
</div>
<div class="place-card-meta">
<div class="inline-row-gap1-5">
<span class="icon-ms-18">visibility</span>
<span>920</span>
</div>
<div class="inline-row-hover-primary">
<span class="icon-ms-18">chat_bubble</span>
<span>15</span>
</div>
<div class="inline-row-gap2-ml2">
<div class="avatar-xs" data-alt="User avatar placeholder"></div>
<span class="text-main-xs-medium">winter_sea</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="community-list-div-06">
<button class="community-list-button-04">
<span class="icon-ms-20">chevron_left</span>
</button>
<button class="community-list-button-05">1</button>
<button class="icon-btn-ghost">2</button>
<button class="icon-btn-ghost">3</button>
<span class="community-list-span-06">...</span>
<button class="icon-btn-ghost">12</button>
<button class="community-list-button-06">
<span class="icon-ms-20">chevron_right</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
</main>

  {{>partials/chatbot}}
  {{>partials/footer}}
  {{>partials/scripts}}
</body>
</html>
